lead_paragraph: Claudio Ranieri re-named himself The Thinkerman on Thursday as he reflected on masterminding Leicester City's improbable rise from relegation candidates to Premier League champions.

headline.print_headline: I Am The Thinkerman Now, Says Leicester Mastermind Ranieri
